Project Overview
Beyaz Masa, complaint desk of Istanbul Metropolitan Municipality, is constantly loaded with volumes of complaints written for various matters via different platforms. Only in May 2020, Beyaz Masa received complaints of almost a million which report problems ranging from broken pipes to buses running late. In addition, particularly thorough Twitter, irrelevant and political content is addressed to the municipality accounts which unnecessarily divert attention of workers at Beyaz Masa.

